Federation 

Finland         67          43,002        Israel        81      52,107 

France          66          833,139       Kuwait        98      25,453 

Greece          75          81,140        Nigeria       83      1,403 

Ireland         83          45,033        Pakistan      99      3,200 

Italy           50          324,197       Turkey        86      140,190 

