<H3> <TI>   May Inflation Rate Steady; Prices Unchanged </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    May Inflation Rate Steady; Prices Unchanged </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2106195694 </F>
<F P=103> PA2106195694 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
BFN 

    [Editorial Report] San Salvador EL DIARIO DE HOY in Spanish 
on 17 June on page 12 reports the Economy Ministry's General 
Directorate of Statistics and Census has reported that prices 
remained unchanged and that inflation was kept in check during 
May. According to a communique from that office, the average 
inflation rate is 0.82 percent for the first five months of 1994. 

</TEXT>

