<H3> <TI>   Eight Leave Chilean Consulate Voluntarily </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Eight Leave Chilean Consulate Voluntarily </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2306232694 Havana PRENSA LATINA in Spanish 2237 GMT 23 Jun 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PA2306232694 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana PRENSA LATINA </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Havana, 23 Jun (PL) -- A group of eight people, who 
had illegally occupied the Chilean consulate in this capital to 
force their departure from the country, voluntarily left the 
diplomatic mission this afternoon. Sources close to the 
consulate confirmed to PRENSA LATINA that the occupants left the 
mission at 1730 (2130 GMT) aboard two vehicles with diplomatic 
license plates and that they were taken to their respective 
homes by official Chilean personnel. 

