<H3> <TI>   Mulino Announces Special Flights for Haitians </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Mulino Announces Special Flights for Haitians </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2306173194 Panama City LA ESTRELLA DE PANAMA in Spanish 23 
Jun 94 p 36 </F>

<F P=103> PA2306173194 </F>
<F P=104>  Panama City LA ESTRELLA DE PANAMA </F>
